{"tid":1787417,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巿民聖誕願望「煲底見」","createTime":"2019-12-18T02:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T02:10:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"68651ebfe1efec26696deda1d15a159a8b70f668","tid":1787417,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:09:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191218/G7VHUWV6IUSHEQ477WZM6JG5S4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191218%2FG7VHUWV6IUSHEQ477WZM6JG5S4%2F&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BujHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=5e4f3581\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191218%2FG7VHUWV6IUSHEQ477WZM6JG5S4%2F&h=c7d22586\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191218/G7VHUWV6IUSHEQ477WZM6JG5S4/</a><br />\n<br />\n巿民聖誕願望「煲底見」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「茫茫圍城的顛簸，層層燎原的星火，重燃原來消失的感覺&hellip;&hellip;」今年硝煙特別多，香港人不耽於吃喝玩樂，寧去遊行不去旅行，逆權運動步入第一個聖誕，香港人會如何度過？<span style=\"color: orange;\">不少市民寫下聖誕願望：「除罩煲底見！」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576601256_02c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576601256_02c1.jpg&h=8ef682da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民主女神和師弟稱會與香港一起度過這聖誕。朱家駿攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留港支持抗爭<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：社區放TG 「如攻擊市民」<br />\n<br />\n往年早在11月，一眾商場聖誕裝飾已「整裝待發」，但今年直到12月中，聖誕氣氛仍未見濃烈，商場外不見排隊購物的人龍，只見「光復香港，時代革命」等口號的文宣、塗鴉，證明港人未忘抗爭。過往聖誕是旅遊旺季，今年不少港人決定留港度過，與手足齊上齊落。中學生師弟（化名）本來預備聖誕節去日本旅行，但6月已決定取消，笑指「習慣（慳錢）咗就好，想留啲錢，畀下啲衝衝子。」中學生黃同學指今年寧願留港度假，「我哋仲有好多個聖誕，但係香港如果冇就冇咗。」深信香港人應該做香港事，「你都係住喺香港，即係你冇可能漠視佢哋，自己走咗去旅行，我所有時間都會留畀手足。」<br />\n<br />\n抗爭運動期間一直配合政府提早收車的港鐵，昨日宣佈將在平安夜及除夕夜通宵服務，當日下午起加強列車服務，額外增加逾七百班車。九巴亦將於平安夜、聖誕日及除夕夜加強服務，疏導乘客。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃翠儀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b36acba01fb4255640e1bf69cb84f99681bac4","tid":1787417,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6BiBqu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6BiBqu.jpg&h=76ab2b42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdw2RCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdw2RCH.jpg&h=8da8b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}